ournament.%20Afghanistan%20play%20their%20final%20group%20game%20against%20West%20Indies%20on%20June%2018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fpeeping-from-behind-the-camera-playful-rashid-khan-told-to-shut-up-by-fazalhaq-farooqi-watch%2Farticleshow%2F111000053.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Dead%2C%201%2C200%20Stranded%20In%20Sikkim%20After%20Cloudburst%20Triggers%20Flash%20Floods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIncessant%20rains%20caused%20by%20a%20cloudburst%20in%20Sikkim's%20Mangan%20district%20-%20measuring%20over%20220.1%20mm%20-%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20killed%20six%20people%2C%20the%20state's%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20state's%20tourism%20department%2C%20over%201%2C200%20domestic%20tourists%20and%2015%20foreign%20nationals%20-%2010%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20three%20from%20Nepal%2C%20and%20two%20from%20Thailand%20-%20are%20stranded%20in%20the%20Lachung%20village%2C%20some%2050%20km%20from%20Mangan%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Secretary%20VB%20Pathak%20has%20initiated%20talks%20with%20the%20Centre%20to%20airlift%20the%20stranded%20tourists%20if%20weather%20conditions%20remain%20clear.%20Alternatively%2C%20they%20will%20be%20evacuated%20by%20road%20-%20although%2C%20it%20may%20take%20a%20week%20to%20restore%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20landslides%20in%20Mangan%20District%2C%20Pakshep%20and%20Ambhithang%20have%20been%20badly%20affected%20with%20six%20casualties%20and%20some%20injuries%20reported.%20A%20relief%20camp%20has%20been%20set%20up%20in%20Pakshep.%20The%20state%20has%20announced%20relief%20for%20victims'%20families.%20The%20Mangan%20District%20Administration%20has%20been%20informed%20to%20issue%20relief%20funds%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pathak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20evacuating%20the%20stranded%20tourists%20from%20Lachung%2C%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20facing%20difficulties%20in%20road%20communication%20at%20six-seven%20places%20due%20to%20active%20landslides.%20It%20will%20take%20us%20around%20five%20to%20seven%20days%20to%20restore%20the%20roads%2C%20with%20directions%20emitted%20to%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organization%20and%20the%20state%20PWD.%20Hence%2C%20the%20state%20has%20sent%20a%20requisition%20for%20airforce%20helicopters%20for%20evacuation%2C%20depending%20on%20weather%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pathak%20also%20assured%20that%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bno%20threats%20to%20glacial%20lakes%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20National%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%20is%20continuously%20observing%20and%20monitoring%20over%2015%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20Sikkim.%20There%20is%20no%20threat%20as%20such.%20The%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%20and%20CDAC%20are%20working%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20state%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Department%20and%20sharing%20important%20data.%20There%20is%20no%20potential%20threat%20of%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20flood%20during%20the%20monsoon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20looming%20threat%20of%20rising%20levels%20of%20the%20Teesta%20River%20in%20the%20low-lying%20areas%2C%20Mr%20Pathak%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20lots%20of%20sediments%20in%20the%20Teesta%20River%20after%20the%20GLOF%2C%20resulting%20in%20rising%20water%20levels.%20Hence%2C%20even%20in%20the%20regular%20monsoonal%20showers%2C%20the%20water%20levels%20are%20rising.%20We%20are%20taking%20up%20these%20concerns%20with%20the%20ministry%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamages%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20places%20near%20Mangan%20and%20not%20from%20Lachen%2C%20Lachung%2C%20or%20Chungthang.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Dzongu's%20Sankalang%20village%2C%20a%20newly%20laid%20bailey%20suspension%20bridge%2