mencing%20the%20academic%20session.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SANJAY%20SHARMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Feducation%2Fnews%2Fbseb-bihar-deled-result-2024-declared-on-secondary-biharboardonline-com-check-direct-link-here%2Farticleshow%2F110999756.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Meets%20Zelensky%2C%20Macron%20At%20G7%2C%20Will%20Hold%20Talks%20With%20Pope%2C%20Meloni%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20summit%20is%20being%20held%20at%20the%20luxurious%20Borgo%20Egnazia%20resort%20in%20Italy's%20Apulia%20region.%20India%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20the%20G7%20Summit%20as%20an%20Outreach%20country%20and%20this%20is%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20overseas%20visit%20since%20he%20took%20oath%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20third%20straight%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20held%20bilateral%20meetings%20with%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak.%20He%20will%20hold%20talks%20with%20several%20other%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20Pope%20and%20Italian%20PM%20Giorgia%20Meloni.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Zelenskyy%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20it%20was%20a%20productive%20one%20and%20that%20India%20is%C2%A0eager%20to%20further%20cement%20bilateral%20relations%20with%20Ukraine.%20On%20the%20war%20with%20Russia%2C%C2%A0the%20PM%20reiterated%20that%20India%20believes%20in%20a%20human-centric%20approach%20and%20that%20the%20way%20to%20peace%20is%20through%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiving%20details%20of%20the%20PM's%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Macron%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20Spokesperson%C2%A0Randhir%20Jaiswal%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BTaking%20Strategic%20Partnership%20to%20new%20levels!%20PM%20%40narendramodi%20met%20President%20%40EmmanuelMacron%20of%20France%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%2050th%20G7%20Summit%20in%20Apulia%2C%20Italy%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20leaders%20discussed%20ways%20to%20further%20strengthen%20the%20partnership%20including%20in%20areas%20of%20defence%2C%20nuclear%2C%20space%2C%20education%2C%20climate%20action%2C%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20critical%20technologies%2C%20connectivity%20and%20culture.%20They%20also%20exchanged%20views%20on%20key%20global%20and%20regional%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDay%20one%20of%20the%20summit%20was%20dominated%20by%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20as%20the%20leaders%20agreed%20on%20a%20US%20proposal%20to%20back%20a%20%24%2050-billion%20loan%20to%20Kyiv%20utilising%20frozen%20Russian%20assets%2C%20described%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20outcome%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20his%20departure%20statement%2C%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bglad%26quot%3B%20that%20his%20first%20foreign%20visit%20in%20his%20third%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20to%20Italy%20for%20the%20G7%20Summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BI%20warmly%20recall%20my%20visit%20to%20Italy%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202021.%20Prime%20Minister%20Meloni's%20two%20visits%20to%20India%20last%20year%20were%20instrumental%20in%20infusing%20momentum%20and%20depth%20in%20our%20bilateral%20agenda.%20We%20remain%20committed%20to%20consolidate%20the%20India-Italy%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20and%20bolster%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20and%20the%20Mediterranean%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20her%20opening%20address%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20G7%20leaders%2C%20Ms%20Meloni%20said%20southern%20Italy%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20venue%20to%20send%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20the%20Global%20South.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20we%20are%20hosting%20the%20summit%20in%20Apulia.%20We%20did%20this%20because%20Apulia%20is%20a%20region%20of%20southern%20Italy%20and%20the%20message%20we%20want%20to%20launch%20is%20that%20the%20G7%2C%20under%20the%20Italian%20presidency%2C%20wishes%20to%20strengthen%20its%20dialogue%20with%20the%20nations%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EItaly%20is%20India's%20fourth-largest%20trading%20partner%20in%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20with%20bilateral%20trade%20worth%20%2415%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718366460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fem8552ng_pm-modi-zelensky-_650x400_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-meets-macron-rishi-sunak-at-g7-will-hold-talks-with-pope-meloni-5889009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20in%20Italy%20for%20the%20G7%20Summit%2C%20where%20he%20is%20holding%20a%20series%20of%20key%20bilateral%20meetings%20with%20world%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-meets-macron-rishi-sunak-at-g7-will-hold-talks-with-pope-meloni-5889009%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Story%20Of%20Kamal%20Ram%3A%20Indian%20Soldier%20Who%20Helped%20Liberate%20Italy%20In%20WW2%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20Italy%20today%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20G7%20summit.%20This%20is%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20first%20foreign%20visit%20after%20taking%20charge%20for%20the%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20G7%20group%20but%20has%20been%20invited%20to%20the%20summit.%20Its%20participation%20is%20significant%20as%20a%20'voice%20of%20the%20global%20south'%2C%20a%20term%20that%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20reiterated%20in%20the%20past.%20During%20the%20Second%20World%20War%2C%20Indian%20soldiers%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20campaign%20of%20the%20Allied%20forces%20to%20liberate%20Italy%20from%20Benito%20Mussolini's%20Fascist%20regime%20and%20Nazi%20Germany.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2050%2C000%20Indian%20soldiers%20fought%20in%20Italy%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%20Six%20of%2020%20Victoria%20Crosses%2C%20Britain's%20highest%20gallantry%20award%2C%20given%20to%20soldiers%20in%20the%20Italian%20theatre%20of%20war%20were%20conferred%20on%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Heroics%20Of%20Sepoy%20Kamal%20Ram%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Allied%20invasion%20of%20Europe%20to%20liberate%20occupied%20countries%20from%20the%20Nazis%20and%20Fascist%20Italy%20began%20in%201943.%20The%20D-Day%20landings%20in%20Normandy%20in%201944%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20liberation%20of%20France.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20recruited%20young%20men%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20to%20fight%20in%20some%20of%20the%20most%20hostile%20battlefields.%20Young%20Kamal%20Ram%2C%20who%20would%20have%20been%2018%2C%20volunteered%2C%20and%20joined%20the%208th%20Punjab%20Regiment%20of%20the%20British%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20portrait%20of%20Sepoy%20Kamal%20Ram%20with%20the%20Imperial%20War%20Museum%20%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20portrait%20of%20Sepoy%20Kamal%20Ram%20with%20the%20Imperial%20War%20Museum%20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F1i1rnn2_sepoy-kamal-ram_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20portrait%20of%20Sepoy%20Kamal%20Ram%20with%20the%20Imperial%20War%20Museum%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Image%3A%20IWM%20(Art.%20IWM%20ART%20LD%204516)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Orbat%20or%20Order%20of%20Battle%20was%204th%2C%208th%20and%2010th%20Infantry%20Divisions%20would%20be%20deployed%20to%20liberate%20Italy.%20Kamal%20Ram's%20regiment%20was%20part%20of%20the%208th%20Infantry%20Division.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Germans%20and%20Italians%20had%20built%20multiple%20fortifications%20called%20the%20Gustav%20Line%20which%20ran%20from%20the%20Tyrrhenian%20Sea%20in%20the%20west%20to%20the%20Adriatic%20Sea%20east.%20The%208th%20Infantry%20Division%20arrived%20in%20Italy%20via%20Syria%20in%20September%201943.%20Young%20Indians%2C%20who%20were%20just%2018%20and%20some%20were%2016%2C%20from%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20volunteered%20to%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2012%2C%201944%2C%20the%208th%20Punjab%20Regiment%20assaulted%20the%20Gustav%20Line.%20Just%20after%20crossing%20the%20River%20Gari%2C%20his%20company%20was%20surrounded%20by%20four%20German%20machine%20gun%20positions%20on%20the%20front%20and%20flanks.%20Securing%20the%20post%20was%20crucial%20to%20defend%20a%20bridgehead.%20The%20company%20commander%20asked%20for%20volunteers%20to%20secure%20the%20post%20by%20outflanking%20the%20enemy%20from%20the%20right%2C%20Sepoy%20Kamal%20Ram%2C%2019%2C%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20crawled%20through%20the%20barbed%20wire%20and%20attacked%20the%20enemy%20position%20through%20a%20flank.%20He%20killed%20a%20German%20soldier%2C%20silencing%20the%20machine%20gun.%20When%20another%20German%20tried%20to%20seize%20his%20weapon%2C%20in%20close%20combat%2C%20Kamal%20Ram%20killed%20him%20with%20his%20bayonet%20attached%20to%20the%20rifle.%20A%20German%20officer%2C%20to%20Sepoy%20Ram's%20surprise%2C%20emerged%20from%20the%20trenches%20and%20shot%20him%20dead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20moved%20to%20the%20second%20machine%20gun%20position%2C%20which%20was%20holding%20the%20company's%20advance.%20He%20lobbed%20grenades%20and%20silenced%20the%20enemy%20guns%20and%20the%20remaining%20enemy%20surrendered.%20He%20moved%20forward%20to%20assist%20a%20company%20Havildar%20who%20was%20attacking%20the%20third%20gun%20position%20and%20covered%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20post.%20He%20single-handedly%20took%20control%20of%20two%20machine%20gun%20positions%20and%20helped%20take%20on%20the%20third.%20The%20display%20of%20courage%20was%20vital%20to%20secure%20the%20bridgehead%20and%20establish%20two%20bridges%20for%20the%20incoming%20forces%20to%20cross%20the%20river.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20when%20a%20platoon%20moved%20forward%2C%20Germans%20hiding%20in%20a%20house%2C%20fired%20on%20the%20incoming%20troops.%20Sepoy%20Kamal%20Ram%20dashed%20toward%20the%20house%2C%20killed%20one%20German%20and%20captured%20two%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20service%2C%20King%20George%20VI%2C%20pinned%20a%20Victoria%20Cross%2C%20the%20highest%20gallantry%20award%2C%20to%20Sepoy%20Kamal%20Ram's%20chest%20on%20May%2027%2C%201944%2C%20in%20Italy.%20He%20was%20the%20second%20youngest%20Indian%20to%20be%20awarded%20the%20Victoria%20Cross.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Official%20Gazette%20notification%20archived%20by%20The%20National%20Archives%2C%20Kew%2C%20UK%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Official%20Gazette%20notification%20archived%20by%20The%20National%20Archives%2C%20Kew%2C%20UK%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fsepgn4t8_sepoy-kamal-ram_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20Gazette%20notification%20archived%20by%20'The%20National%20Archives'%2C%20Kew%2C%20UK%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESepoy%20Kamal%20Ram%20continued%20to%20serve%20in%20the%208th%20Punjab%20Regiment%20until%20it%20was%20transferred%20and%20merged%20with%20the%20Baloch%20regiment%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20post-independence.%20He%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20after%20Independence%20and%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20rank%20of%20Honor