%20should%20have%20been%20given%20was%20stopped%20by%20God%20due%20to%20arrogance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20none%20amongst%20those%20who%20opposed%20Ram%20were%20given%20power.%20All%20of%20them%20together%20were%20made%20number%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20follows%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat's%20statement%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20said%20that%20a%20true%20'sevak'%20should%20serve%20people%20without%20arrogance%20and%20maintain%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20pray%20to%20Ram%20should%20be%20humble...%20Lord%20Ram%20does%20not%20discriminate%20and%20does%20not%20punish.%20Ram%20delivers%20justice%20to%20everyone.%20He%20gives%20and%20continues%20giving%20to%20all.%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20always%20just%20and%20will%20remain%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718359620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fimn43fvo_rss-leader-indresh-kumar-ians_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-against-lord-ram-came-2nd-arrogant-stopped-at-241-senior-rss-leader-5887895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20ideologue%20Indresh%20Kumar%20has%20said%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20as%20a%20feeling%20of%20arrogance%20had%20taken%20over%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20ended%20at%20Number%202%20position%20for%20being%20anti-Ram.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-against-lord-ram-came-2nd-arrogant-stopped-at-241-senior-rss-leader-5887895%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-against-lord-ram-came-2nd-arrogant-stopped-at-241-senior-rss-leader-5887895%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthose-against-lord-ram-came-2nd-arrogant-stopped-at-241-senior-rss-leader-5887895%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Darshan%20Case%20Victim%20Died%20Of%20Shock%2C%20Haemorrhage%2C%20Reveals%20Post-Mortem%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20tortured%20and%20killed%20allegedly%20by%20popular%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%20died%20of%20shock%20and%20haemorrhage%2C%20according%20to%20the%20autopsy%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autopsy%20found%2015%20wounds%20on%20the%20body%20of%20Renuka%20Swamy%2C%20who%20was%20allegedly%20beaten%20to%20death%20by%20the%20actor%20and%20his%20aides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20kidnapped%20Renuka%20Swamy%20from%20Karnataka's%20Chitradurga%20over%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20social%20media%20posts%20of%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20the%20girlfriend%20of%20Mr%20Thoogudeepa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenuka%20Swamy's%20body%20bore%20wounds%20and%20marks%20on%20the%20head%2C%20abdomen%2C%20chest%20and%20other%20parts.%20The%20autopsy%20report%20indicated%20his%20head%20rammed%20a%20mini%20truck%20parked%20in%20a%20shed%20in%20Bengaluru%20where%20he%20was%20brought%20from%20Chitradurga.%20The%20police%20have%20seized%20this%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20recovered%20wooden%20logs%2C%20a%20leather%20belt%2C%20and%20a%20rope%20used%20to%20torture%20Renuka%20Swamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thoogudeepa%20had%20allegedly%20planted%20three%20men%20to%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20murder%2C%20but%20during%20interrogation%2C%20they%20were%20exposed%2C%20the%20police%20have%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20offered%20the%20three%20Rs%205%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20heinous%20crime.%20He%20(Darshan%20Thoogudeepa)%20has%20to%20face%20the%20consequences...%20there%20will%20be%20no%20interference%20from%20the%20government.%20There%20is%20no%20room%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Karnataka%20Health%20Minister%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20a%20driver%20identified%20as%20Ravi%2C%20who%20had%20taken%20Renuka%20Swamy%20from%20Chitradurga%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20200%20km%20apart%2C%20surrendered%20before%20the%20police.%20Another%20accused%2C%20Raghu%20alias%20Raghavendra%2C%20had%20along%20with%20others%20arranged%20Ravi's%20taxi%20and%20boarded%20it%20in%20Chitradurga%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20went%20into%20hiding%20after%20dropping%20them%20off%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Later%2C%20he%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20taxi%20association%20in%20Chitradurga%2C%20who%20told%20him%20to%20surrender%20to%20the%20police%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghu%20ran%20a%20fan%20club%20of%20the%20Kannada%20actor%20in%20Chitradurga.%20The%20actor%20hired%20him%20to%20gather%20information%20about%20Renuka%20Swamy%2C%20the%20police%20had%20said.%20Renuka%20Swamy's%20wife%20alleged%20he%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20near%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20and%20his%20aides%20dumped%20the%20body%20by%20a%20road.%20A%20food%20delivery%20rider%20saw%20the%20body%20and%20called%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20footage%20shows%20two%20cars%20-%20one%20of%20them%20linked%20to%20Mr%20Thoogudeepa%20-%20leaving%20the%20area%20after%20dumping%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718359500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdu6rm6ng_kannada-actor-darshan-_625x300_11_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-case-victim-died-of-shock-haemorrhage-reveals-post-mortem-report-5888756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20tortured%20and%20killed%20allegedly%20by%20popular%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%20died%20of%20shock%20and%20haemorrhage%2C%20according%20to%20the%20autopsy%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-case-victim-died-of-shock-haemorrhage-reveals-post-mortem-report-5888756%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20Spies%20Went%20Undercover%20In%20Gaza%20To%20Find%20Hostages%20Captured%20By%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camp%20is%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20deep%20inside%20Palestinian%20territory.%20It%20was%20in%20one%20of%20the%20camp's%20many%20markets%20that%20Hamas%20had%20kept%20Israeli%20woman%20Noa%20Argamani%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20woman%20who%20had%20been%20dramatically%20captured%20on%20video%20pleading%20for%20her%20life%20while%20being%20taken%20into%20Gaza%2C%20as%20hostage.%20Unbeknownst%20to%20Ms%20Argamani%20and%20three%20other%20hostages%20in%20the%20area%2C%20Israeli%20commandos%20had%20infiltrated%20the%20camp%20to%20launch%20a%20daring%20rescue%20operation%20to%20free%20them%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2F06%2F09%2Fisrael-gaza-hostages-rescue-raid%2F%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2011%20am%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20rescue%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20burst%20into%20the%20apartment%20where%20Ms%20Argamani%20was%20being%20held%2C%20declaring%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20being%20rescued!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescue%20mission%2C%20which%20also%20freed%20Almog%20Meir%20Jan%2C%2022%2C%20Andrey%20Kozlov%2C%2027%2C%20and%20Shlomi%20Ziv%2C%2041%2C%20was%20marked%20by%20intense%20preparation%20and%20military%20engagement.%20Planned%20for%20weeks%2C%20the%20operation%20involved%20thousands%20of%20troops%2C%20advanced%20technological%20support%2C%20and%20precise%20execution%20the%20report%20says.%20Israeli%20intelligence%2C%20with%20US%20assistance%2C%20%C2%A0analysed%20digital%20data%2C%20drone%20footage%2C%20and%20communications%20intercepts%20to%20locate%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20upon%20confirming%20the%20hostages'%20location%20in%20Nuseirat%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20constructed%20detailed%20mock-ups%20of%20the%20buildings%20to%20rehearse%20the%20rescue.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20this%20preparation%20echoed%20the%20famed%20Operation%20Entebbe%20of%201976%2C%20a%20counter-terrorism%20operation%20in%20Uganda%20initiated%20in%20response%20to%20the%20hijacking%20of%20an%20international%20civilian%20flight%20operated%20by%20Air%20France%20on%20its%20route%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20Paris.%20Despite%20the%20daylight%20timing%20of%20the%20raid%20posing%20higher%20risks%2C%20Israeli%20military%20strategists%20deemed%20it%20the%20best%20chance%20for%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20break%20of%20morning%2C%20the%20mission%20was%20kicked%20off.%20IDF%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Herzi%20Halevi%20and%20other%20top%20security%20officials%20monitored%20from%20a%20command%20room.%20Special%20forces%20disguised%20in%20undercover%20vehicles%2C%20including%20a%20truck%20mimicking%20a%20civilian%20commercial%20vehicle%20and%20a%20white%20Mercedes%20loaded%20with%20furniture%2C%20approached%20the%20target%20area.%20Eyewitnesses%20described%20the%20sudden%20eruption%20of%20gunfire%20as%20Israeli%20soldiers%20engaged%20Hamas%20militants%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2F06%2F09%2Fisrael-gaza-hostages-rescue-raid%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20initial%20success%20in%20rescuing%20Ms%20Argamani%20without%20alerting%20her%20guards%2C%20complications%20arose%20with%20the%20other%20hostages.%20A%20firefight%20broke%20out%2C%20transforming%20the%20covert%20raid%20into%20a%20full-blown%20conflict.%20The%20rescue%2C%20though%20ultimately%20successful%20in%20retrieving%20the%20hostages%2C%20left%20a%20trail%20of%20devastation.%20According%20to%20Gaza%20health%20officials%2C%20over%20270%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%2C%20including%20civilians%20caught%20in%20the%20crossfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rescued%20hostages%20were%20eventually%20flown%20to%20safety%2C%20with%20the%20mission's%20success%20hailed%20by%20Israeli%20authorities%20despite%20the%20heavy%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20251%20people%20seized%20by%20Hamas%2C%20seven%20captives%20have%20been%20freed%20alive%20by%20Israeli%20forces.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20116%20hostages%20still%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%2041%20whom%20the%20army%20believes%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%2C%20the%20deadliest%20in%20Gaza's%20history%2C%20began%20with%20a%20deadly%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20on%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20resulting%20in%201%2C189%20Israeli%20deaths%20and%20252%20hostages%20taken.%20Israel's%20response%20has%20been%20relentless%2C%20with%20the%20Gaza%20Health%20Ministry%20reporting%20over%2037%2C232%20deaths%2C%20mostly%20civilians.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718358480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fkp31s5sg_gaza-reuters-_625x300_14_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camp%20is%20located%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20deep%20inside%20Palestinian%20territory.%20It%20was%20in%20one%20of%20the%20camp's%20many%20markets%20that%20Hamas%20had%20kept%20Noa%20Argamani%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20Israeli%20woman%2C%20as%20hostage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-israel-commandos-infiltrated-gaza-to-rescue-hostages-in-daring-mission-5888548%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20UN%20warned%20of%20cross-border%20female%20genital%20mutilation%20threat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718357166000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110994641%2Cimgsize-1323664.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhy-un-warned-of-cross-border-female-genital-mutilation-threat%2Farticleshow%2F110994541.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110994541.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20human%20rights%20office%20on%20Friday%20warned%20that%20the%20global%20fight%20against%20female%20genital%20mutilation%20was%20being%20undermined%20by%20families%20crossing%20borders%20to%20have%20girls%20undergo%20the%20procedure.%20A%20report%20by%20the%20U.N.%20rights%20office%20found%20that%20some%20families%20in%20countries%20where%20the%20practice%20is%20banned%20were%20travelling%20to%20neighbouring%20states%20or%20further%20afield%20where%20it%20was%20legal%20or%20where%20law%20criminalising%20it%20were%20not%20enforced.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhy-un-warned-of-cross-border-female-genital-mutilation-threat%2Farticleshow%2F110994541.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhy-un-warned-of-cross-border-female-genital-mutilation-threat%2Famp_articleshow%2F110994541.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhy-un-warned-of-cross-border-female-genital-mutilation-threat%2Famp_articleshow%2F110994541.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Congress's%20New%20Dilemma%3A%20Will%20Rahul%20Agree%20to%20Be%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F718j3mb8_rahul-gandhi-yatra_120x90_28_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongresss-top-body-cwc-passes-resolution-for-rahul-gandhi-to-be-leader-of-opposition-report-5845184%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%3C%2Fa%3E%20dilly-dallying%20in%20accepting%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee's%20(CWC)%20June%208%20unanimous%20decision%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-results-2024-will-rahul-gandhi-be-leader-of-opposition-what-sonia-gandhi-said-5847066%5C%22%3Eleader%20of%20the%20opposition%3C%2Fa%3E%20(LoP)%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20highlights%20a%20grievous%20chink%20in%20the%20armour%20of%20the%20grand%20old%20party%3A%20indecisiveness.%20Having%20been%20acknowledged%20as%20the%20face%20of%20the%20campaign%20that%20propelled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-results-live-video-congress-worker-hugs-rahul-gandhi-outside-aicc-headquarters-as-party-leads-on-100-seats-5815008%5C%22%3ECongress%20from%2052%20to%2099%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rahul%20ought%20to%20have%20promptly%20thanked%20the%20party%20for%20reposing%20faith%20in%20him%20and%20accepted%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20party%20general%20secretary%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20a%20trusted%20aide%20of%20Rahul%2C%20said%20post%20the%20meeting%20was%20that%20after%20having%20heard%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20members%2C%20he%20would%20take%20a%20decision%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoPs%20In%20The%20Past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20of%20LoP%20has%20existed%20in%20India's%20parliamentary%20system%20since%20the%20days%20of%20the%20Central%20Legislative%20Assembly%20in%20British%20India.%20Motilal%20Nehru%20held%20that%20position%20in%201923.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20delay%20legislation%2C%20including%20finance%20bills%2C%20of%20the%20Raj.%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%20never%20held%20the%20position.%20Nehru%20was%20a%20three-term%20Prime%20Minister%3B%20Indira%20Gandhi%20lost%20power%20and%20also%20failed%20to%20get%20elected%20in%201977.%20Thus%2C%20during%20the%20Janata%20Party's%20rule%2C%20Yashwantrao%20Chavan%20and%20C.M.%20Stephen%20functioned%20as%20LoP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20leader%20to%20be%20formally%20recognised%20as%20LoP%2C%20a%20party%20in%20opposition%20requires%20a%20minimum%20of%2010%25%20of%20the%20total%20strength%20of%20the%20House.%20Until%20the%20Congress%20split%20in%201969%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20no%20LoP.%20Ram%20Subhag%20Singh%20of%20the%20Congress%20(O)%20was%20accorded%20this%20recognition%20in%201969%20when%20more%20than%2010%25%20of%20MPs%20joined%20the%20exodus%20against%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20However%2C%20the%20privilege%20of%20an%20LoP%20getting%20the%20status%20and%20facilities%20of%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20had%20to%20wait%20until%201977%2C%20when%20the%20Janata%20regime%20of%20Morarji%20Desai%20amended%20the%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-man-of-match-should-be-leader-of-opposition-shashi-tharoor-5838913%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Rahul%20Gandhi%20'Man%20Of%20The%20Match'%2C%20Should%20Be%20Leader%20Of%20Opposition%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20LoP%20in%201989-90%3B%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20took%20turns%20as%20LoP%20between%201990%20and%201996.%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20served%20in%20that%20position%20for%20a%20fortnight%20during%20Vajpayee's%20short-lived%20premiership.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20was%20the%20Congress%20party's%20LoP%20for%20just%20over%20a%20year%20in%201998%20before%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20took%20over%20the%20party's%20reins%20and%20also%20became%20LoP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20(1999-2004).%20During%20the%20decade%20of%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20rule%20(2004-2014)%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20were%20the%20LoPs%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20Eyes%20On%20Rahul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20as%20no%20party%20has%20had%20a%2010%25%20share%20-%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20got%2044%20seats%20in%202014%20and%2052%20in%202019%20-%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament%20in%202014%20(Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20and%202019%20(Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury)%20were%20not%20accorded%20LoP%20status.%20However%2C%20for%20purposes%20of%20selecting%20key%20government%20positions%2C%20where%20the%20statute%20requires%20consultation%20with%20LoP%2C%20they%20were%20invited%20to%20selection%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Congress%20bouncing%20back%20with%2099%20seats%20(the%20strength%20has%20since%20grown%20to%20101%20with%20two%20independents%2C%20both%20Congress%20members%20before%20polls%2C%20joining%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament)%2C%20the%20decade-long%20'banishment'%20is%20now%20over%2C%20and%20the%20party%20is%20looking%20towards%20Rahul%20to%20be%20its%20face%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%20As%20An%20MP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rahul%20accepts%20the%20job%2C%20it%20will%20require%20his%20presence%20in%20Parliament%20for%20most%20days%20of%20a%20session.%20His%20attendance%20as%20an%20MP%2C%20both%20from%20Amethi%20and%20Wayanad%2C%20between%202004-2019%2C%20has%20not%20been%20too%20encouraging.%20He%20went%20on%20sojourns%20abroad%20when%20Parliament%20was%20in%20session%2C%20and%20his%20record%20in%20asking%20questions%20and%20participating%20in%20debates%20has%20been%20dismal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20campaign%2C%20Rahul%20boasted%20about%20his%20knowledge%20of%20the%20government%20system%20as%20an%20insider%20for%20years.%20The%20real%20test%20awaits%20him%20now%3A%20to%20provide%20effective%20leadership%20to%20the%20232%20INDIA%20bloc%20MPs%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20heads%20a%20coalition%20of%20293-member%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-wayanad-raebareli-question-rahul-gandhis-both-will-be-happy-remark-5876846%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0On%20Wayanad-Raebareli%20Question%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3BBoth%20Will%20Be%20Happy%26quot%3B%20Remark%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20worthwhile%20to%20recall%20a%20note%20in%20the%20diary%20maintained%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20de%20facto%20number%20two%20in%20her%20last%20dispensation%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20views%20of%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20became%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20have%20been%20recorded%20in%20Sharmishtha%20Mukherjee's%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EPranab%2C%20My%20Father%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20%5BRahul%5D%20has%20all%20the%20arrogance%20of%20his%20Nehru-Gandhi%20lineage%20without%20their%20political%20acumen...Maybe%20politics%20isn't%20his%20calling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20LoP%2C%20Rahul%20will%20have%20to%20follow%20rules%20and%20procedures.%20Frequent%20absences%20from%20House%20proceedings%20will%20not%20go%20down%20well.%20LoP%20has%20to%20be%20cautious%20and%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Sonia%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%20dilemma%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20facing%20another%20crunch%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20After%20Sonia%20became%20the%20party%20President%20in%201998%2C%20the%20Congress%20constitution%20was%20amended%20to%20provide%20that%20the%20party%20chief%20shall%20be%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament%2C%20even%20if%20he%20or%20she%20is%20not%20an%20MP.%20Sonia's%20election%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%201999%20saw%20her%20occupying%20both%20posts%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%20Though%20she%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20Congress%20President%20or%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20being%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20she%20has%20now%20been%20re-elected%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhi-re-elected-as-congress-parliamentary-party-chairperson-5846946%5C%22%3Echairperson%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Parliament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Thus%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20party%20chief%2C%20will%20be%20the%20LoP%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20with%20Sonia%20adorning%20the%20front%20benches%20of%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20indeed%20becomes%20the%20LoP%2C%20he%20may%20like%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20parliamentary%20legacy%20of%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20original%20Rae%20Bareli%20MP%20(1952%2C%201957)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dust%20the%20records%20of%20his%20great-great-grandfather%2C%20Motilal%20Nehru%2C%20who%20as%20the%20LoP%20could%20stall%20and%20delay%20legislation%20of%20the%20British%20Raj%20in%201923.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliament%20of%20India's%20first%20successful%20scam-busting%20was%20done%20by%20Feroze%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20then-finance%20minister%20in%20February%201958.%20The%20then%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20could%20not%20find%20fault%20with%20Feroze%20Gandhi's%20well-researched%2C%20articulated%20diatribe%2C%20which%20was%20carried%20out%20as%20per%20parliamentary%20rules%20