ole%20in%20January%20-%20for%20a%20seventh%20time%20in%20just%2010%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Rahim%20in%20his%20petition%20said%20he%20needed%20the%20parole%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20programme%20hosted%20by%20the%20Dera%20Sacha%20Sauda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20admitting%20his%20petition%2C%20the%20high%20court%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%20and%20the%20Sikh%20Gurdwara%20Prabandhak%20Committee%20(SGPC)%2C%20and%20sought%20a%20reply%20by%20July%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20on%20January%2029%20had%20raised%20questions%20over%20repeated%20paroles%20granted%20to%20the%20rape%20convict%20who%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20serving%2020%20years%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20ordered%20the%20Haryana%20government%20to%20take%20its%20permission%20if%20he%20approaches%20for%20parole%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20SGPC%2C%20the%20court%20had%20also%20ordered%20the%20state%20government%20to%20give%20information%20on%20how%20many%20people%20have%20been%20given%20parole%20in%20this%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20there%20had%20been%20a%20pattern%20behind%20granting%20paroles%20to%20the%20rape%20convict%2C%20and%20it%20usually%20happened%20during%20state%20or%20local%20body%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDera%20followers%2C%20and%20particularly%20those%20of%20Ram%20Rahim%20Singh%2C%20are%20influential%20in%20Punjab's%20Malwa%20region%2C%20with%20their%20votes%20seen%20as%20key%20in%20deciding%20parliamentary%20and%20legislative%20elections.%20The%20Malwa%20region%20has%2069%20constituencies%20-%20over%20half%20of%20the%20Punjab%20assembly's%20117%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDera%20followers%20-%20who%20number%20in%20the%20crores%20and%20have%20been%20relatively%20subdued%20since%20Rahim%20Singh%20was%20jailed%20-%20are%20widely%20seen%20as%20voting%20per%20diktats%20from%20sect%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3