0Crorepati.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20work%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20and%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20have%20been%20felicitated%20with%20several%20awards%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20name%20a%20few%2C%20in%202015%2C%20the%20foundation%20was%20honoured%20with%20the%20British%20Medical%20Association%20South%20Asia%20Award%20for%20establishing%20a%20cadaver%20programme%20in%20India.%20In%202021%2C%20he%20was%20given%20the%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20from%20Grant%20Thornton%20Sabera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20received%20the%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%C2%A0Excellence%C2%A0Awards%20for%20Community%20Service.%20The%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20also%20received%20the%20%E2%80%98Best%20NGO%20Award%E2%80%99%20in%202023%20from%20NOTTO%2C%20DGHS%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20National%20Organ%20Donation%20Day.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sunil%20Shroff%20receiving%20Dr%20K%20C%20G%20Verghese%20Excellence%20Awards%202023.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-300x134.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receiving-Dr.-K.C.G.-Verghese-Excellence-Awards-2023_11zon-1717420609-500x223.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDr-Sunil-Shroff-receivi