-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAmla-trees-at-the-farm_11zon-1717158064-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351732%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20amla%20(gooseberry)%20trees%20lining%20the%20farm.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20been%20far%20from%20smooth.%20%E2%80%9CWater%20availability%20is%20a%20critical%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Namita%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20in%20a%20hilly%20area%20with%20a%20non-perennial%20river%20nearby%2C%20water%20scarcity%20is%20a%20significant%20challenge.%20This%20is%20a%20primary%20reason%20why%20many%20people%20around%20us%20are%20abandoning%20their%20agricultural%20lands.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20create%20canals%20for%20water%20supply%2C%20Namita%20notes%20that%20there%20is%20still%20a%20severe%20shortage%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20summer%20months.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20exploring%20rainwater%20harvesting%20as%20a%20potential%20solution%20to%20create%20a%20reliable%20source%20of%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20Namita%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20sincerely%20hope%20that%20the%20water%20situation%20improves.%20While%20the%20river%20has%20some%20water%20at%20certain%20points%2C%20other%20areas%20remain%20completely%20dry.%20We%20believe%20that%20if%20the%20government%20addresses%20this%20issue%20earnestly%2C%20it%20will%20not%20only%20benefit%20us%20but%20also%20many%20others%20who%20wish%20to%20pursue%20farming%20with%20greater%20ease%20and%20happiness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298011%2Fgurugram-retired-woman-starts-ayurvedic-veena-jis-hair-oil-business-to-reduce-hair-fall%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bl