erindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739-150x264.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-22-at-10.13.23-PM_11zon-1716443739.jpeg%20910w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350879%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22879%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMayank%20Sharma%20has%20cultivated%20a%20thriving%20terrace%20garden%20in%20his%20Delhi%20apartment%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Mayank%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20make%20all%20the%20arrangements%20for%20bees%20and%20other%20pollinators%20to%20be%20attracted%20to%20the%20flowers.%20But%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20about%20the%20male%20flowers.%E2%80%9D%20He%20terms%20the%20period%20between%202015%20and%202020%20as%20his%20biggest%20learning%20curve.%20It%20was%20only%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic-induced%20lockdown%20that%20gardening%20went%20from%20being%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F226879%2Forganic-terrace-gardening-fight-depression-mother-kitchen-heartwarming-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20passion%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Mayank%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20was%20born%20during%20this%20period%20and%20it%20got%20me%20thinking%20about%20how%20the%20air%20we%20breathe%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20best%2C%20and%20neither%20is%20the%20food%20we%20eat%20the%20healthiest.%20I%20began%20thinking%20deeply%20about%20the%20world%20we%20were%20bringing%20our%20kids%20into%20and%20decided%20to%20be%20better.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20corollary%20of%20that%20thought%20is%20the%20kitchen%20garden%20that%20Mayank%20has%20cultivated.%20Filled%20with%20every%20kind%20of%20local%20vegetable%20as%20well%20as%20seasonal%20produce%2C%20the%20garden%20he%20says%20is%20an%20e